---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy | CreativAudio">
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-text-body text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        At CreativAudio, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. We offer a fair and transparent refund policy for all our digital products.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-2">Eligibility</h2>
      <p>
        You are eligible for a refund if you contact us within <strong>14 days</strong> of your order and have <strong>not yet downloaded</strong> your product. Once a product has been downloaded or 14 days have elapsed, we cannot offer a refund.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-2">How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p>
        To request a refund, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info.creativaudio@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">info.creativaudio@gmail.com</a> with your order number and the email address used for the purchase. We will process your refund within 5-7 business days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-2">Non-Refundable Cases</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <li>The product has already been downloaded.</li>
        <li>More than 14 days have passed since the date of purchase.</li>
        <li>The refund request does not include valid order information.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-2">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our refund policy, reach out to us at <a href="mailto:info.creativaudio@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">info.creativaudio@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
